headline: 2 Reasons to Like VRSK (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the past six months, Verisk’s shares (currently trading at $265.69) have posted a disappointing 10.2% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 5% gain. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
